sources.style.sass:
$black:#000000
$blue:#1D3557
$lightblue:#355070

$purple:#4E356E
$lighpurple:#535CA9
$white: #ffffff
$lightgray:#c4c4c4
$darkgray: #666666
@font-face
    font-family: "beba"
    src: url("../Fonts/BebasNeue-Regular.ttf") format("truetype")
*
    margin: 0px
    padding: none
    scroll-behavior: smooth
body
    font-family: Atkinson Hyperlegible
.grid-container
    display: grid
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1140px 1fr
    grid-template-rows: 80px 580px 0.4fr 0,6fr
.nav-bar
    color: $white
    display: grid
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1140px 1fr
    grid-template-rows: 80px
    grid-column: 1/-1
    grid-row: 1
    align-items: center
    background: #355070
    box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)
#nav-logo
    grid-column: 2
    grid-row: 1
    justify-items: start
    font-weight: bold
    font-size: 24px
#nav-links
    display: flex
    justify-content: flex-end
    grid-column: 2
    grid-row: 1
    .nav-link-flexcontainer
        display: flex
        width: 715px
        justify-content: space-between
        a
            text-decoration: none
            color: $white
            font-family: Inter
            font-size: 20px
.hero-slider
    display: grid
    overflow-y: hidden
    overflow-x: hidden
    grid-row: 2/3
    grid-column: 1/-1
    height: 580px
    // background-image: url("../Images/heroimg.png")
    background-color: $lighpurple
.hero-text
    margin-top: 14vh
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', cursive
    width: 700px
    margin-left: 9.5vw
    font-size: 96px
    line-height: 115px
    letter-spacing: 0.02em
    color: #FFFFFF
.Benchmark-info
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    grid-column: 2
    margin-top: 50px
#Info-header
    color: $blue
    font-weight: bold
    font-size: 34px
#Info-body
    margin-top: 4vh
    color: $lightblue
    width: 720px
    font-size: 20px
    font-weight: 400
.Info-Image-container
    color: $blue
    width: 400px
    height: 400px
    background: #C4C4C4
#Studentinfo-wrapper
    display: grid
    grid-column: 2/3
    grid-row: 4
    margin-top: 50px
.Studentinfo
    background-color: $lightblue
    display: flex
    height: 300px
    padding: 20px 0px
#Studentinfo-container
    color: $white
    margin-left: 40px
    margin-top: 30px
    font-weight: bold
    font-size: 34px
#Studentinfo-para
    margin-right: 200px
    margin-top: 20px
    width: 330px
    font-weight: 500
    font-size: 16px
    margin-bottom: 5vh
.Studentinfo-button
    font-weight: bold
    font-size: 14px
    background-color: #666666
    text-decoration: none
    padding: 10px
    color: $blue
    background-color: $white
.Studentimages
    display: flex
    flex-wrap: wrap
    margin-top: 2%
.Studentimage1
    margin-right: 14px
    margin-bottom: 10px
    width: 120px
    height: 120px
    background-color: $white
.E-Portal-info
    display: flex
    justify-content: space-between
    grid-column: 2
    margin-top: 50px
    margin-bottom: 50px
.atags
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    margin-top: 40px
.borderbuttonlogin
    z-index: -888
    margin-top: -3vh
    margin-left: 0.4vw
    width: 140px
    height: 31px
    border: 1.5px solid $blue
.login
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: center
    width: 120px
    height: 31px
    background-color: $lightblue
.Signup
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: center
    margin-top: 30px
    width: 118px
    height: 31px
    background-color: $lightblue
#Login
    font-weight: 700
    font-size: 14px
    text-decoration: none
    color: $white
#Signup
    font-weight: 700
    font-size: 14px
    text-decoration: none
    color: $white

.E-portal-header
    color: $blue
    font-weight: bold
    font-size: 34px
.E-Info-body
    color: $lightblue
    width: 720px
    font-size: 20px
#E-Image-container
    width: 400px
    height: 400px
    background-color: #c4c4c4
.student-slider
    display: grid
    grid-row: 6
    grid-column: 2/3
    background-color: pink
    width: 1140px
    height: 300px
    margin-bottom: 40vh
#wrapper
    width: 100%
    max-width: 1140px
    position: relative
#carousel
    overflow: auto
    scroll-behavior: smooth
    scrollbar-width: none
#prev,
#next
    z-index: 999
    display: flex
    justify-content: center
    align-content: center
    background: white
    border: none
    padding: 8px
    border-radius: 50%
    outline: 0
    cursor: pointer
    position: absolute

#prev
    top: 50%
    left: 0
    transform: translate(50%, -50%)
    display: none
#next
    top: 50%
    right: 0
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%)
#content
    display: grid
    grid-gap: 16px
    grid-auto-flow: column
    margin: auto
.item
    width: 300px
    height: 300px
